298
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,410
Help me figure this out.

299
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:49,120
Today, Zhu Yifei

300
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,240
was supposed to come for a deal.

301
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,030
Halfway through the transaction,

302
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:51,870
