312
00:15:02,030 --> 00:15:03,790
The moment they walked in, they started
grabbing the phone and beating me up.

313
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:05,000
In my own house, for god's sake,

314
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:05,840
