315
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,170
and gave me 3 judo chops.

316
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,240
And in the end,

317
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:10,160
Zhang Yi'ang showed up too.

318
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:19,840
Tell me—

319
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:23,490
