screw me over here?

320
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:24,900
Zhu Yifei,

321
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:26,970
those two perverts,

322
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,250
or Zhang Yi'ang?

323
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:33,240
Maybe...

324
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:33,960
Speak Chinese!

325
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,220
They're all possible!

326
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:52,800
Call Lang Bowen.

327
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:58,720
Why call him at a time like this?

328
00:16:00,410 --> 00:16:01,670
He caused the trouble,

329
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:04,160
so have him clean up his own mess.

330
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:05,840
Okay.

331
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,320
Rong,

332
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,480
