333
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,120
Do I sound like

334
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:18,360
I'm joking?

335
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,560
So it really happened, Rong?

336
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,530
How could it be?

337
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,840
What do you want me to do then?

338
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,390
Figure it out yourself.

339
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,000
Rong?

340
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:45,120
Rong?

341
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,400
[Fang Yong]

342
00:17:09,829 --> 00:17:10,640
Sorry,

343
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,310
