347
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,130
Please try again later.

348
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,130
What's going on?

349
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,030
You guys...

350
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:31,250
Gathering together, huh?

351
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:33,510
Letting Liu Bei ran away just like that!

352
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,790
With so many of you there!

353
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:35,920
Trying to hide, huh?

354
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:38,030
You didn't even notice a thing.

355
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:39,780
You didn't even notice a thing!

356
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,350
There are 9 bianzhong in total,

357
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:42,440
