358
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:44,160
We're only missing a small one, right?

359
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,490
So I think the loss
is still under control!

360
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:53,580
"The loss is under control."

361
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:56,810
The loss is under control?

362
00:17:58,270 --> 00:17:59,520
Those 9 are a set.

363
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:00,760
