368
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:09,560
Who do you expect me to sell
the other one to?

369
00:18:18,580 --> 00:18:20,240
Alright, I heard everything.

370
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,510
Why do this?

371
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:24,010
They are all honest kids.

372
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:25,790
We're a family.

373
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:28,080
We're a team,

374
00:18:28,110 --> 00:18:29,070
