375
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:31,860
Who did you hit?

376
00:18:32,590 --> 00:18:33,590
For talking back.

377
00:18:34,350 --> 00:18:34,960
Get up.

378
00:18:37,830 --> 00:18:38,630
Go take a rest.

379
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:43,940
