380
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:54,110
Uncle.

381
00:18:55,010 --> 00:18:57,550
[Pinghe] [Liu Bei's location]

382
00:18:55,350 --> 00:18:56,840
Do you think Liu Bei

383
00:18:57,070 --> 00:18:58,930
