385
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,880
He must be taken care of.

386
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,320
Zheng, oh Zheng.

387
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,080
They all say

388
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:12,030
