397
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,750
When I checked the phone,

398
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,680
the tracker was moving.
What does that tell us?

399
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:40,440
Liu Bei can't get away.

400
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:43,720
Where are you going?

401
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:45,310
Trying to kill him in broad daylight?

402
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:45,830
Wait,

403
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,180
