404
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:50,310
Of course we'll kill him,

405
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:52,510
and it will be bloody.

406
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:56,210
Let's chop him into pieces.

407
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:58,850
You bring him here,

408
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,280
and I'll do the chopping.

409
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,450
Okey-dokey.

410
00:20:15,430 --> 00:20:17,880
[Police]

411
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:22,700
What are you doing?

412
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,380
My neck hurts.

413
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:28,490
Go to the hospital if it hurts.

414
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:30,130
Go do your work.

415
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,580
[Baoku Fresh Produce Delivery Center]

416
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:06,250
Come on, let's have a meeting.

417
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:13,510
Guys,

418
00:21:14,180 --> 00:21:15,710
