that she didn't act on her own.

432
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,480
From the time you got into his car

433
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:42,440
to the time you entered Zhou Rong's house,

434
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,570
so much time passed.

435
00:21:43,790 --> 00:21:45,270
Why didn't you contact the bureau?

436
00:21:45,270 --> 00:21:46,270
I wanted to,

437
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:49,760
but my phone got smashed the moment

438
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:50,930
I got in the car.

439
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,030
Captain Wang, you forgot.

440
00:21:52,030 --> 00:21:53,130
I tried to call her,

441
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:54,550
but you didn't let me.

442
00:21:54,690 --> 00:21:55,510
Song Xing!

443
00:21:55,790 --> 00:21:56,240
You see,

444
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,400
I just called Li Qian,

445
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,400
but she suddenly hung up on me.

446
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,200
I wanted to ask what was going on,

447
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,400
but now I can't get through to her.

448
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,600
Is this really the time to be doing that?

449
00:22:09,110 --> 00:22:10,400
Let's put this matter aside for now.

450
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,660
Let it slide, alright?

451
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:13,760
Let's talk about the case instead.

452
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,650
According to the report

453
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:17,720
from our colleagues
staking out Zhou Rong's villa,

454
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,890
after we left,

455
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,720
the security team from Zhou Rong's company

456
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,250
and Hu Jianren rushed over.

457
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:25,240
This shows that the intelligence
provided by Li Qian

458
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,150
was correct,

459
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,570
that Zhou Rong had indeed been robbed.

460
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,940
Li Qian, tell everyone

461
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:32,240
