466
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,750
They were both wearing maid outfits

467
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:40,830
and had their faces covered.

468
00:22:40,830 --> 00:22:43,070
They actually dared to break into
Zhou Rong's house and rob him.

469
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,310
I'm afraid they're no ordinary people.

470
00:22:44,310 --> 00:22:45,040
Chief Zhang.

471
00:22:45,590 --> 00:22:46,440
Could they be those 2 people

472
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,500
who killed Lin Kai?

473
00:22:52,630 --> 00:22:56,440
[September 3, 2012]

474
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,940
Judging from their builds

475
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:02,790
and gaits,

476
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,250
they did look like them.

477
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:20,680
Captain Wang, what are your thoughts?

478
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,970
Tell us what you think.

479
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:26,090
If we try to cover everything at once,

480
00:23:26,090 --> 00:23:28,150
we definitely won't have enough manpower.

481
00:23:28,150 --> 00:23:30,150
We need to keep monitoring Zhou Rong

482
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:31,710
and keep searching for

483
00:23:31,790 --> 00:23:32,990
Liu Bei and Zhu Yifei.

484
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,160
But I think the main focus

485
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,720
should be on those 2 robbers.

486
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:37,480
Because the phone is in their hands,
after all.

487
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,200
That phone is definitely

488
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,890
the key to cracking this case.

489
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:41,500
I disagree.

490
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:44,590
I think the key should be Liu Bei.

491
00:23:46,070 --> 00:23:46,610
Li Qian.

492
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:48,160
Regarding the matter

493
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:48,920
of you going undercover,

494
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:49,570
I...

495
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,110
It was my mistake.

496
00:23:51,110 --> 00:23:52,310
I... I apologize to you.

497
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:53,200
But don't bring your emotions

498
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,250
