503
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:00,960
Then why is it not Lang Bowen?

504
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:01,620
Keep quiet.

505
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:02,640
But

506
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:03,160
why

507
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,200
can't it be Lang Bowen?

508
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,110
It should be Liu Bei.

509
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:05,840
The robbers.

510
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:06,480
Question:

511
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:10,380
