521
00:24:29,790 --> 00:24:31,560
If that student's IQ

522
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,490
is lower than Class A's average

523
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:36,610
but higher than Class B's average,

524
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,030
then after he transfers,

525
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:39,160
the average IQ of both classes

526
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,020
will increase.

527
00:24:42,550 --> 00:24:43,200
Correct.

528
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,330
So the key is

529
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,930
the one with the highest IQ?

530
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:47,680
Wrong.

531
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:49,310
It's the one who poses the greatest threat

532
00:24:49,310 --> 00:24:50,550
to society among those people.

533
00:24:50,550 --> 00:24:51,110
Wrong.

534
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:53,200
Wait, what does this have

535
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,310
to do with the case?

536
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:55,450
Nothing at all.

537
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:56,860
I just said that

538
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:57,690
to break

539
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:58,850
