545
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,460
Why?

546
00:25:09,550 --> 00:25:11,400
The phone is in the robbers' hands now.

547
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,200
Why not follow

548
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:13,960
