549
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:14,750
Because those two

550
00:25:14,750 --> 00:25:16,150
had their faces covered.

551
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,440
And ever since Lin Kai's incident,

552
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:18,550
