572
00:25:41,270 --> 00:25:43,160
I presume it was because of Liu Bei.

573
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,140
Could it be

574
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:46,300
that Liu Bei took the bianzhong away?

575
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:48,190
If that was really the case,

576
00:25:48,790 --> 00:25:49,830
then neither Zhou Rong nor Zhu Yifei

577
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,830
would let him off.

578
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,560
His life might be in danger.

579
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:54,400
We have to find him as soon as possible.

580
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:56,320
